THe design of the program:
	
	
	String : initialiseApplet() 
		Method to do the following things:
			1) assign upload link.
			2) assign password
			3)	assign login link
	String : authenticate()
			1) log in the server using the password.
			
	String: download()
			1) input a link and download the file from the link.
			2) take care of the open save as dialog box
			
			
	String: upload()
			1) take care of the open file dialog
			2) upload the file on to the server.
			
			
			content-length - j * 